Ahem.</p>
<p>Re Smith and Jones and food chain: that is indeed what I had in mind.<br />
My thoughts for saying Agent a lot was that they were in the middle of a puddle of local cops, so were being a bit stiff. This isn&#8217;t clear, though, and on rereading I do feel a bit too Agented.</p>
<p>Thanks, man! <span class='wp-smiley wp-emoji wp-emoji-smile' title=':)'>:)</span></p>
